Oxenfree was a 10/10 game. If you're looking for a 3D imersive spooky platformer, this game is definitely for you. It really scared me psychology! caption.text:
Mighty No. 9!!! 💥💥💥
An Action Platform Game Created By Comcept And Inti Creates In 2016 For Pretty Much Every Platform Available (With More Promised That Never Came Out... But That’s Another Story)! 😀
The Game Was One Of The Most Highly Anticipated Kickstarter Projects To Surface During The Late 2010s Boom Of The Platform, Envisioned As The Spiritual Successor Of Mega Man (Who’s Franchise Was In A Well Publicized Hiatus At The Time) And Was Headed By Longtime Series Producer And Artists Keiji Inafune (Who Is Often Misattributed As The Father Of The Character)! 😁
The Kickstarter Was A Huge Success And Everything Looked Great... And Then It Went Horribly Wrong In So Many Ways (Honestly It’s A Pretty Lengthy Story In Itself That Has Been Well Documented Elsewhere)! 🤷‍♂️
In The End The Game Ended Up Failing To Meet Expectations And Is Seen As A Failure, But In All Honesty It’s Not A Terrible Game Just A Fairly Average One And With The Release And Success Of Mega Man 11 In 2018 It Seems To Have Fallen Completely Into Obscurity. 😌 
#mightyno9 #mightynumber9 #comcept #inticreates #deepsilver #actionplatformer #platformgame #platformer #runandgun #kickstartercampaign #kickstarter #kickstartergames #playstation4 #keijiinafune #retrogaming #gamingcollection #gaming
